{"tid":2417660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣將翻拍《梨泰院Class》韓網友力挺兩大男神出演：許光漢&劉以豪","createTime":"2021-02-22T05:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T22:06:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4e931bccb5e69925da8aa342b3d3bb10fd22ce","tid":2417660,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_2988bae8f8a78094df0b44737a5b67d3/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-21/133811-897557.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_2988bae8f8a78094df0b44737a5b67d3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-21%2F133811-897557.jpg&h=6b7a0b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n栗子頭超難駕馭的，兩位都很優質！你心中的最佳人選是誰呢～？<br />\n<br />\n由朴敘俊、金多美主演的熱門漫改劇《梨泰院Class》將翻拍成台版，製作團隊則是台劇《我們與惡的距離》、《做工的人》的「大慕影藝」，堅強後盾讓人非常放心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_dea4e3f6e28b013a274db0797deda3a4/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-21/133811-897558.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_dea4e3f6e28b013a274db0797deda3a4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-21%2F133811-897558.jpg&h=608af2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖源：我們與惡的距離 The World Between Us@FB）<br />\n<br />\n目前韓方也公開了對於選角傾向找台灣一線男星，且在韓國要有知名度的演員，雖然皆在討論中，還未定案，但韓國網友已經討論的相當熱烈。<br />\n<br />\n能夠飾演「朴世路」這個角色，呼聲最高的兩位男演員&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1fe170f56e85c4b866a2c01adbe46446/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-21/133811-897559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1fe170f56e85c4b866a2c01adbe46446%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-21%2F133811-897559.jpg&h=9150445e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖源：JTBC drama@FB）<br />\n<br />\n▼被韓國網友視為台灣男神的「劉以豪」，參加過節目《超人回來了》以及《街頭美食鬥士第二季》，還和李昇基合作過《Twogether》的旅遊節目，在韓國知名度跟好感度都非常高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fc36c4d9c2c4ebadabd26ea54aae2a09/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-21/133811-897560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fc36c4d9c2c4ebadabd26ea54aae2a09%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-21%2F133811-897560.jpg&h=60063074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖源：劉以豪 Jasper@FB）<br />\n<br />\n▼再來就是以熱門台劇《想見你》成為新一代國民男友的「許光漢」，在韓播出後人氣飆升，引發熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1612477256fbd053b3a3928e8c30387f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-02-21/133811-897561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1612477256fbd053b3a3928e8c30387f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-02-21%2F133811-897561.jpg&h=70a0163a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖源：《想見你》@播出截圖）<br />\n<br />\n這兩位是在韓國網友心中的兩大人選，雖然還很難想像造型是栗子頭的模樣，但如果是他們其中一位接下，肯定又會掀起一波熱潮，實在是讓人太期待啦！！！"},{"pid":"2954f578a3065a38ae71c50108bf13743d25a728","tid":2417660,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:23:05.000Z","msg":"兩邊互相翻拍...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8b7de8760adf40da59bbe218f69fa8c2733707","tid":2417660,"uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"爛尾劇都要翻拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"116468b13dd9dd235bc95f5dd7e138fc69d8a387","tid":2417660,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"栗子頭唔係個個得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4ea5e2d5920d7b2741340cb6bf7c5a2b7fe07c","tid":2417660,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c8b7de8760adf40da59bbe218f69fa8c2733707","tid":2417660,"uid":21141,"